    "Techniques such as decision trees, neural networks, and support vector machines have been employed to enhance the accuracy and efficiency of intrusion detection systems.",
    "Additionally, AI and ML play a crucial role in malware detection, enabling the identification of new threats and adaptive responses to changing patterns.",
    "• Threat hunting-Traditionally, cyber security heavily relied on signature-based techniques to detect threats.",
    "While effective against known threats, these techniques struggle to promptly identify and respond to novel, unidentified dangers that do not match known signatures.",
    "This is where the power of Artificial Intelligence comes into play."
